                  <msItem>
                     <p> ROLLRIGHT. Copy (indented) of a charter by which <persName>
                           <forename>William</forename>, the
               prior</persName>, and the <orgName key="org_109039">convent of St. Frideswide</orgName> grant to the 
               <orgName key="org_109071">prior and canons of Norton</orgName> the whole of their land 'in hamello' in
               <placeName key="place_109460">Rollendrith</placeName>, and also that virgate of land in <placeName key="place_109206">Churchull</placeName> 
               which they had of the gift of <persName>
                           <forename>Baldwin</forename> de <surname>Paries</surname>
                        </persName>,
               paying annually for the same 27s. 6d. 
               Dated <origDate when="1248">1248</origDate>, on the morrow of SS. Simon and Jude. 
               [Wigram no. 1006] 
               . </p>
